content.html: Tell me why then is the average price per gallon in the UK $5.79? Or France $5.54? Why is it $6.76 USD in Canada? Biden has nothing to do with it. It’s the oil comapnies being greedy. Plain and simple. No amount of blaming Biden will change that. Holding those responsible will.
